OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as pottery
OL,4,Cmanufacturer Denby goes into
OL,5,Cadministration
OL,7,FThe iconic pottery manufacturer Denby
OL,8,Fhas gone into administration, putting
OL,9,Fhundreds of jobs at risk.
OL,11,FDenby Pottery, established in 1809,
OL,12,Fbased near Ripley in Derbyshire,
OL,13,Fannounced on Tuesday 31 March that it
OL,14,Fhad gone into formal administration.
OL,16,F500 people are employed by the
OL,17,Fmanufacturer, with 350 of them based
OL,18,Fin the Derbyshire factory.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
