OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775070658
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as pottery
OL,4,Cmanufacturer Denby goes into
OL,5,Cadministration
OL,7,FAfter 217 years, the firm said it had
OL,8,Fentered "challenging times" and
OL,9,F"enormous financial challenges" with
OL,10,Freduced spending from customers,
OL,11,Fhigher employment costs and surging
OL,12,Fenergy prices.
OL,14,FIt had announced the intended
OL,15,Fappointment of administrators three
OL,16,Fweeks ago, saying it hoped to secure
OL,17,Fnew investors, restructure or face
OL,18,F"closing for good".
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@[O]qD@AOUqD@_O]zD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775070658
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as pottery
OL,4,Cmanufacturer Denby goes into
OL,5,Cadministration
OL,7,FClaire Ward, East Midlands Mayor,
OL,8,Fagreed with the sentiment that, from
OL,9,Fthe outside looking in, nobody
OL,10,Fappeared to be aware of how bad things
OL,11,Fhad become at the company.
OL,13,FShe said she had met with management
OL,14,Fat the site last week in a bid to save
OL,15,Fthe firm, which employs 350 people in
OL,16,FDerbyshire and more than 500 across
OL,17,Fthe company.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775070658
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as pottery
OL,4,Cmanufacturer Denby goes into
OL,5,Cadministration
OL,7,FMs Ward told the Local Democracy
OL,8,FReporting Service: "I did what I am
OL,9,Fencouraging everyone else to do, and
OL,10,Fthat is to buy Denby pottery. Save
OL,11,FDenby.
OL,13,F"It is really important for their
OL,14,Fcashflow at the moment that they get
OL,15,Fin as much money as possible, so
OL,16,Fpeople can help by going and visiting
OL,17,Fand buying Denby pottery.
OL,19,F"There are 350 jobs on that site just
OL,20,Fin the factory and across the company
OL,21,Fit has over 500 jobs.
OL,26,@pD@TOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775070658
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as pottery
OL,4,Cmanufacturer Denby goes into
OL,5,Cadministration
OL,7,F"359,000 people every year visit Denby
OL,8,FPottery Village, it is an absolutely
OL,9,Ffantastic tourist attraction."
OL,11,FCraig Thomson from the GMB union said:
OL,13,F"This is the human cost of Government
OL,14,Finaction; communities let down and
OL,15,Fworkers laid off by companies that
OL,16,Fcan't keep up with the cost of energy.
OL,18,F"There is a very real sense of fury
OL,19,Famongst the Denby workers receiving
OL,20,Fthis news today.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775070658
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as pottery
OL,4,Cmanufacturer Denby goes into
OL,5,Cadministration
OL,7,F"We've been screaming and shouting
OL,8,Fabout the impact the cost of
OL,9,Findustrial energy is having on the
OL,10,Fceramics industry for years.
OL,12,F"Now the time for warm words is over,
OL,13,Fand Ministers must decide if they want
OL,14,Fa British ceramics industry or not.
OL,16,F"Denby is a British icon with history
OL,17,Fdating back over 200 years. We've been
OL,18,Fworking closely with the local MP and
OL,19,Fresidents to make the case that its
OL,20,Ffuture is too important to be left to
OL,21,Fchance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
