OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as pottery
OL,4,Cmanufacturer Denby goes into
OL,5,Cadministration
OL,7,F"GMB is focused on doing everything we
OL,8,Fcan to support and protect these
OL,9,Fworkers during this difficult time".
